name: Elypta AB
businessDescription: Elypta is a Swedish molecular diagnostics company focused on reducing cancer mortality through early detection. Elypta is pioneering a metabolism-based liquid biopsy and measures the GAGome – system biomarkers of tumor metabolism. Machine learning algorithms are then used to detect signatures of cancer noninvasively. Elypta is advancing a broad clinical program across different cancers with the first indication expected to be early detection of recurrence in renal cell carcinoma.
longBusinessDescription:
Elypta is a molecular diagnostic company focused on preventing cancer mortality by developing a liquid biopsy platform for detection and monitoring of the disease. The approach is based on measurement of the complete profile of human glycosaminoglycans as biomarkers of tumor metabolism and use of machine learning algorithms to generate a score against cancer-type specific signatures. Studies have shown exceptional accuracy in renal cell carcinoma and the clinical development program include multiple other indications.
Potential applications include early detection, surveillance of recurrence and monitoring or prediction of treatment response, replacing or complementing medical imaging. Elypta is differentiated by its pan-cancer potential, metabolism-based approach and robust, cost-efficient mass-spectrometry based kits. Several years of research at Chalmers University of Technology in Gothenburg, Sweden, led to the founding of Elypta in the spring of 2017

longBusinessDescription:
The Kind Socks is the global fashion brand dedicated to conscious and colorful socks. A conscious brand with a digital approach, we have reimagined a classic sock in a fun conscious way - giving this everyday essential sock the love it deserves.

OUR SOCKS
1. FASHIONABLE FOREVER
We feel that sustainability starts off with the design philosophy. We strive to
make beautiful socks, designed and inspired by fashion and the seasons. Our
designs are fashionable and timeless at the same time. Since our socks last very
long, creating designs that are fashionable forever is key.
2. FINEST ORGANIC COMBED COTTON
Climate change is one of the biggest themes of our era. Therefore, sustainability is
at the core of our brand. We are not perfect, but trying every day to be as
sustainable as we can be. That’s why we use organic combed cotton, which is
certified by GOTS, the Global organic textile standard (GOTS).
3. DURABLE
Because they are made from quality and as-natural-as-possible materials, our
socks will last you a long time and will not rip after just a few wears.
4. STYLE WITH KINDNESS
Style with Kindness means to be careful with our environment, and trying to
keep our footprint as small as possible. To us this also means innovation and
teaming up with like-minded businesses and organization to achieve this. Impact
is something we make together. Good thing there are many companies working
towards the same goal.

longBusinessDescription:
Workaround can help you whether you want to renegotiate your existing lease or are looking for new premises! Our matchmaking team will look at your current and future needs, after which we match your requirements with office solutions on the market today and off-the-market solutions.
Workaround's service is free of charge for prospective tenants as our landlords pay us to market their solutions. Our driving force is to quickly find the right office at the best possible price for you as a tenant since our ambition is to be a trusted partner every time your office needs change. In the last five years alone, almost 30% of our matchmaking come from return customers.
Our four-step process is well proven with over 1 000 successful brokerings in the last five years.
1. Vision. We create a mutual understanding of your office needs and convert your greater vision into clearly defined criteria for our search.
2. Matching. We match your vision and criteria against currently available office solutions and off-the-market premises. We list a number of potential office solutions and evaluate together.
3. Viewings. We perform an initial inspiration tour in order to further narrow down the list of potential offices. 1-3 additional viewing tours follow in order to select the best possible solution.
4. Negotiation and Contracts. Workaround support throughout negotiations up to contract signing. When needed, Workaround will support with hand over to interior design and office services partners.

Memory capacity and bandwidth are the most difficult bottlenecks in computing systems. ZeroPoint's technology compresses main memory losslessly in real-time by a factor of 2-4x, providing a significant increase in memory capacity and bandwidth. As a result, the system is substantially faster with cheaper CAPEX and OPEX. Servers and embedded systems based on ARM, RISC-V, and Intel processor architectures get greater performance per watt.
Globally, servers consume roughly 1% of all available electricity, with that percentage expected to rise to 5% in the next few years. ZeroPoint has created a solution that allows servers to consume significantly less energy. A typical data centre consumes 1 terawatt-hour per year.

name: Innoscentia
businessDescription: Innoscentia develop sensor based analogue and digital indicators of real time food status to prolong shelf and consumption time, thereby reducing waste costs and food waste. Our sensors come in forms of labels possible to attach to the package and can show the level of freshness either visually directly on the label or through a digital system in your smartphone or a larger system if you are eg a retailer.
longBusinessDescription:
Currently about 19% of all meat produced is wasted before reaching the consumer and the negative environmental impact of this wasted part represents more than 1,5 times the emissions from the aviation industry. About 10% of the total waste in the meat industry can be derived from confusion or poor use of best before dates resulting in waste to a value of 20 billion USD annually on a global scale. Innoscentia develops smart sensors labels to help solve this.
The basis of the sensors is an ink with the ability to measure gas concentration within a food package. The gas concentration has a direct correlation with the bacterial growth and can therefore provide an indication of the freshness of the product.
The labels aim to prolong the shelf life of meat products and activate the full consumption period resulting in less waste. A prolonged shelf life of only 2 days could reduce retail waste with up to 50% and household waste with up to 60% which would result in massive benefits.
tags: food tech, food waste, cleantech, innovation

longBusinessDescription:
Gaia Grow System makes it possible for every urban individual to grow their own range of vegetables, herbs and medical plants at home without using soil: On the balcony, in the backyard or in the living room, all year round. Packed with nutrition and vitamins one may live a healthier life and enjoy the possibility to organize your very own garden even though you don't have access to any land at all.
Gaia Grow System is a modular system and the most versatile urban gardening equipment for urban environment in a truly sustainable and high yielding set up. We offer a plug and play package which can be assembled in 30 minutes. Add fresh water and you're ready to start growing.
No more transportation of your tomatoes from far away, no more chemicals like pesticides or herbicides. The hydroponic growing technique is also three times quicker and you only use 1/10 of fresh water. Its automatic and the tomatoes taste wonderful.
A solar panel driven Gaia could be placed anywhere, e.g. in regions to combat malnutrition or starvation or places where it is impossible to grow the traditional way. Gaia is uniquely designed, versatile and developed first of all for urban people or local urban small to middle size greenhouse companies.
Three single floor standing Gaia with 5 grow boxes each catering for 45 plants takes only 1 square meter surface area which represents more than 50 square meter in traditional farming. In a greenhouse set up Gaia is capable to produce estimated
48kg/sqm/year of leafy greens or herbs.
Our 5year revenue forecast have 3M fifth year with a gross margin of 78%. Needed investment first year is 1,5M. We predict a positive cash flow as of the third year.
Our vision is to turn 100.000 consumer worldwide to become Gaia growers and equip 100 commercial small to middle size urban greenhouse companies.
Our business idea is based on providing an outstanding piece of Scandinavian designed equipment, impeccable manufactured in new bio plastics and innovative and recyclable materials.
Marketing strategy includes cutting edge marketing technology within digital communication, customer support focused on high class service and support, and Gaia College which will educate a new generation how to use hydroponic growing technology in an online education set up.
Short term goal is 20.000 Gaia consumer equipment sold and also supporting various help organizations operating in i.e. poverty or malnutrition areas.
PPM available on request www.getgaia.com Instagram: growwithgaia

longBusinessDescription:
Är ert företag ute efter en ny lokal? MatchOffice erbjuder ett kostnadsfritt, snabbt och enkelt sätt att hitta lediga lokaler i Sverige. Här kan du skaffa dig en snabb överblick av lediga företagslokaler inom kontor, industri, produktion och lager.
Sökprofilen hjälper dig att hitta rätt lokal genom att direkt meddela dig om nya hyresobjekt som passar dina kriterier. Skapa en sökprofil och hitta nya lokaler redan idag!
Sök och hitta din nya företagslokal bland alla möjliga slags lokaler till företag. Våra kunder har många olika typer av verksamheter som ställer olika krav på sina företagslokaler. I många fall kan området vara något av det viktigaste för ett företag. Just därför kan du här se allt på ett och samma ställe.
Vi på MatchOffice strävar efter att det ska vara så enkelt som möjligt att hitta och jämföra olika hyresobjekt. Här får du därför gratis åtkomst till samtliga annonser för företagslokaler som finns på vår sida. Det är viktigt för oss att du hittar en bra lokal hos en bra hyresvärd. Just därför hittar du bara hyreslokaler från seriösa hyresvärdar på MatchOffice.
Det vi kan erbjuda dig som oberoende och självständig portal är möjligheten att se flera olika tillgängliga alternativ så att du kan hitta det som passar din verksamhet bäst. Skulle du mot förmodan inte hitta en företagslokal som uppfyller dina krav så kan du snabbt skapa en automatisk och effektiv sökprofil som söker efter objekt som passar dina sökkriterier och bli meddelad när lämpliga lokaler blir tillgängliga.
Anmäl ditt intresse redan idag när du hittar en lokal som väcker ditt intresse. Attraktiva lokaler blir fort uthyrda och då gäller det att vara snabbt ute. Vi hoppas att vi kan hjälpa dig att hitta en företagslokal som passar dig och ditt företag.
